      • setReportDownloadTimeout

        void setReportDownloadTimeout(int reportDownloadTimeout)
        Sets the timeout for both CONNECT and READ to the specified value. Defaults to 3 minutes. Set property api.adwords.reportDownloadTimeout in ads.properties or as a system property to set a default for all ReportDownloaders.
        Parameters:
        reportDownloadTimeout - the reportDownloadTimeout to set in milliseconds
